# When a commit lands, re-check the doc-engine catalog integrity (meta-schema,
# kinds, and every block/doctype definition). docengine runs from this folder,
# so `check` resolves the catalog here. The richer "index staleness" reaction
# (NOTES.md punt #1) swaps in later by changing only this run: line.
on:   [CommitLanded]
mode: react
run:  docengine check
